---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Terms of Service" description="Terms of Service for HolyfireMedia">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20 max-w-4xl">
    <div class="bg-indigo-900/30 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-2xl relative">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-8 border-b border-white/10 pb-6">Terms of Service</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-pink max-w-none text-purple-100 space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Please read these terms of service carefully before using HolyfireMedia. By accessing or using our websites, products, and services, you agree to be bound by these terms.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">1. License and Use</h2>
        <p>
          All karaoke tracks sold on HolyfireMedia are for personal, non-commercial use only. You may not distribute, resell, or publicly perform these tracks without specific permission or licensing. All track rights belong to their respective original copyright holders where applicable.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">2. Digital Downloads</h2>
        <p>
          All products on our store are digital downloads. We do not ship physical products. Upon successful payment, you will receive links to download the files immediately.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">3. Account Integrity</h2>
        <p>
          You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account and password. You agree to accept responsibility for all activities that occur under your account.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For questions regarding these Terms, contact us at: <a href="mailto:jmmusicdistribution@gmail.com" class="text-pink-400 hover:text-pink-300 font-bold">jmmusicdistribution@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
